      <h3>About {author}</h3>
      <p>Success Odyssey Hub explores the intersection of ancient philosophy, modern psychology, and practical strategy to help thoughtful people build lives of meaning, excellence, and lasting achievement. Our research draws from positive psychology, well-being science, Stoic philosophy, and the findings of happiness researchers from Seligman to Kahneman.</p>
