      <h2>Book Recommendations</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Flourish</strong> by Martin Seligman — the definitive account of positive psychology and what genuine well-being actually requires</li>
        <li><strong>The Happiness Advantage</strong> by Shawn Achor — the research case for happiness as a driver of success rather than its consequence</li>
        <li><strong>Flow</strong> by Mihaly Csikszentmihalyi — the psychology of optimal experience and how to design a life rich in meaning and engagement</li>
